						<div class="postbody">I always use 4 bytes per sprite in a metasprite definition, with X and Y being signed values relative to an object's reference point, which is not fixed.<br /><br />I did not use 2's complement for the coordinates though, I used something that simplified out-of-screen tests, but I can't remember what that was right now...</div>

