					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p214009">Re: Metasprite position offsets in regards to player x and y</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=214009#p214009"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Feb 21, 2018 10:16 am&nbsp;</div></td>
